io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>摘要 道可道，非常道；名可名，非常名。无名天地之始，有名万物之母。 是以圣人处无为之事，行不言之教，万物作焉而不辞，生而不有，为而不恃，功成而弗</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>道德经</category><category>心性</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>道德经-马王堆帛书版</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F-%E9%A9%AC%E7%8E%8B%E5%A0%86%E5%B8%9B%E4%B9%A6%E7%89%88/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F-%E9%A9%AC%E7%8E%8B%E5%A0%86%E5%B8%9B%E4%B9%A6%E7%89%88/</guid><description>01 道可道也，非恒道也。名可名也，非恒名也。无名万物之始也，有名万物之母也。故：恒无欲也，以观其眇；恒有欲也，以观其徼。两者同出，异名同谓。玄</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>道德经</category><category>心性</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>道德经-浙江道教协会</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F-%E6%B5%99%E6%B1%9F%E9%81%93%E6%95%99%E5%8D%8F%E4%BC%9A/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F-%E6%B5%99%E6%B1%9F%E9%81%93%E6%95%99%E5%8D%8F%E4%BC%9A/</guid><description>01.道可道，非常道。名可名，非常名。无名天地之始。有名万物之母。故常无欲以观其妙。常有欲以观 其徼。此两者同出而异名，同谓之玄。玄之又玄，众</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>道德经</category><category>心性</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>列子</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%88%97%E5%AD%90/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%88%97%E5%AD%90/</guid><description>摘要 正文 Ref 列子故事 列子文 列子文</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>列子</category><category>冲虚经</category><category>心性</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>庄子</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%BA%84%E5%AD%90/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%BA%84%E5%AD%90/</guid><description>摘要 故事 Ref 庄子</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>庄子</category><category>心性</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>道教神咒</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%81%93%E6%95%99%E7%A5%9E%E5%92%92/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%81%93%E6%95%99%E7%A5%9E%E5%92%92/</guid><description>净心神咒 太上台星，应变无停。 驱邪缚魅，保命护身。 智慧明净，心神安宁。 三魂永久，魄无丧倾。 急急如律令。 净口神咒 丹朱口神，吐秽除氛。舌神正伦，通</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>道</category><category>咒</category></item><item><title>洞玄灵宝定观经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%AE%9A%E8%A7%82%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%AE%9A%E8%A7%82%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>诵读 天尊告左玄真人曰：夫欲修道，先能舍事。 外事都绝，无与忤心。然后安坐，内观心起。若觉一念起，须除灭, 务令安静。 其次，虽非的有贪着，浮游乱想</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>心性</category><category>早晚课</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>高上玉皇心印妙经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%8A%E7%8E%89%E7%9A%87%E5%BF%83%E5%8D%B0%E5%A6%99%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%8A%E7%8E%89%E7%9A%87%E5%BF%83%E5%8D%B0%E5%A6%99%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>上药三品，神与气精，恍恍惚惚，杳杳冥冥. 存无守有，顷刻而成，回风混合，百日功灵。 默朝上帝，一纪飞升，智者易悟，昧者难行。 履践天光，呼吸育清，</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>早晚课</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>黄帝阴符经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%B8%9D%E9%98%B4%E7%AC%A6%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%B8%9D%E9%98%B4%E7%AC%A6%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>上篇 观天之道，执天之行，尽矣。故天有五贼，见之者昌。五贼在心，施行于天。宇宙在乎手，万化生乎身。天性，人也；人心，机也。立天之道，以定人也。</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>阴符经</category><category>早晚课</category><category>心性</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>太上老君说常清静经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E6%B8%85%E9%9D%99%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E6%B8%85%E9%9D%99%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>老君曰：大道无形，生育天地；大道无情，运行日月；大道无名，长养万物；吾不知其名，强名曰道。夫道者：有清有浊，有动有静；天清地浊，天动地静；男</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>清静经</category><category>心性</category><category>早晚课</category><category>炁體源流</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>太上灵宝天尊说禳灾度厄经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%A4%AA%E4%B8%8A%E7%81%B5%E5%AE%9D%E5%A4%A9%E5%B0%8A%E8%AF%B4%E7%A6%B3%E7%81%BE%E5%BA%A6%E5%8E%84%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%A4%AA%E4%B8%8A%E7%81%B5%E5%AE%9D%E5%A4%A9%E5%B0%8A%E8%AF%B4%E7%A6%B3%E7%81%BE%E5%BA%A6%E5%8E%84%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>尔时天尊在禅黎国土，与大道真仙万万亿千人，诸天尊及诸天龙鬼神，尽来集会，受吾约束。世间若有善男子善女人，忽有年灾月厄，游城赤鼠之厄，天罗地网</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>早晚课</category><category>忏悔</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>太上升玄消灾护命妙经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%A4%AA%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87%E7%8E%84%E6%B6%88%E7%81%BE%E6%8A%A4%E5%91%BD%E5%A6%99%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%A4%AA%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87%E7%8E%84%E6%B6%88%E7%81%BE%E6%8A%A4%E5%91%BD%E5%A6%99%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>尔时，元始天尊在七宝林中，五明宫内，与无极圣众，俱放无极光明，照无极世界，观无极众生，受无极苦恼；宛转世间，轮回生死，漂浪爱河，流吹欲海，沉</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>早晚课</category><category>心性</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>文昌帝君阴骘文</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E6%96%87%E6%98%8C%E5%B8%9D%E5%90%9B%E9%98%B4%E9%AA%98%E6%96%87/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E6%96%87%E6%98%8C%E5%B8%9D%E5%90%9B%E9%98%B4%E9%AA%98%E6%96%87/</guid><description>帝君曰：吾(帝)一十七世为士大夫身。未尝虐民酷吏。救人之难，济人之急，悯人之孤，容人之过。广行阴骘[yīn zhì]，上格苍穹。人能如我(帝)</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>文昌帝君阴骘文</category><category>早晚课</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item></channel></rss>